sentences: Daniel de los Reyes (born July 18, 1962) is an American percussionist
He is currently a member of the Zac Brown Band.

In 1997, he played on Steve Winwood's album Junction Seven and Yanni's live recording Tribute; performed with Ricky Martin at the 1999 and 2000 Grammy Awards; and played on Philip Bailey's 2002 LP Soul on Jazz.
